        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Diagnosis of PD according to Gelb et al;

          -  Hoehn & Yahr (H&Y) stage 2.5-3;

          -  Presence of FOG confirmed in the patient assessment prior to participation in the
             study;

          -  Stable pharmacological treatment for the last 8 weeks and during the rehabilitation
             period;

          -  Mini Mental State Examination (MMSE) â‰¥ 24;

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Cardiac, pulmonary, vestibular and orthopedic diseases;

          -  Urinary incontinence;

          -  Severe dyskinesias;

          -  Patients treated with deep brain stimulation;

          -  Visual deficits;

          -  Comorbilities other than PD determining reduction of motor autonomy
